<h1 align="center"> align="center">termisol - the unbreakable terminal emulator</h1>

A cross-platform terminal emulator with AI integration, designed to be crash-proof and feature-complete for power users.

<h2 align="center"> align="center">🚀 features</h2>

<h3 align="center"> align="center">core terminal features</h3>
- **Multi-tab & Split-pane**: Unlimited tabs and flexible split layouts
- **AI Hints**: Contextual AI assistance for commands and errors
- **Command Palette**: Fuzzy search for commands and history
- **Broadcasting**: Send commands to multiple terminals simultaneously
- **GPU Acceleration**: Hardware-accelerated rendering for smooth performance

<h3 align="center"> align="center">Unbreakable Architecture
- **Crash-Proof Session Persistence**: Atomic writes with SHA-256 checksums and backup rotation
- **Service Mode & Auto-Start**: Background service with system tray integration
- **Re-attachable PTY**: Socket-based session management survives GUI restarts
- **Self-Update Mechanism**: Automatic updates with cryptographic verification
- **Robust Error Handling**: Comprehensive crash logging and recovery

<h3 align="center"> align="center">AI Integration
- **Local-First**: Works with Ollama for offline operation
- **Inline Error Explanation**: Non-blocking tooltips explain command failures
- **Natural Language Commands**: "show disk usage" → suggests `du -sh * | sort -rh`
- **Cloud Fallback**: Optional API key configuration for cloud models

<h3 align="center"> align="center">Accessibility
- **Screen Reader Support**: Full TTS integration with system accessibility
- **High Contrast Mode**: Automatic color adjustment for visibility
- **Color Blind Support**: 5 types (protanopia, deuteranopia, etc.)
- **Keyboard Navigation**: Complete keyboard-only operation support

<h3 align="center"> align="center">Professional Integration
- **One-Command Installer**: Automated setup with system integration
- **Linux Desktop Integration**: Systemd services, MIME types, protocol handlers
- **Cross-Platform**: Linux, macOS, Windows with native optimizations

<h2 align="center"> align="center">🛠️ Installation

<h3 align="center"> align="center">Quick Install (Recommended)
```bash
curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/termisol/termisol/main/scripts/install.sh | bash
```

<h3 align="center"> align="center">Manual Install
```bash
<h1 align="center"> align="center">Clone and build
git clone https://github.com/termisol/termisol.git
cd termisol
flutter pub get
flutter build linux

<h1 align="center"> align="center">Install binary
sudo cp build/linux/x64/release/bundle/termisol /opt/termisol/
sudo ln -s /opt/termisol/termisol /usr/local/bin/termisol

<h1 align="center"> align="center">Install desktop integration
sudo cp debian_build/usr/share/applications/termisol.desktop /usr/share/applications/
sudo cp linux/termisol-background.service /etc/systemd/user/
systemctl --user enable termisol-background
systemctl --user start termisol-background
```

<h2 align="center"> align="center">🎯 Usage

<h3 align="center"> align="center">Basic Operations
- `Ctrl+T`: New tab
- `Ctrl+Shift+T`: New window
- `Ctrl+Shift+P`: Command palette
- `Ctrl+Shift+H`: Toggle AI hints
- `Ctrl+Shift+B`: Broadcast mode

<h3 align="center"> align="center">AI Features
- **Error Explanation**: Hover over failed commands for AI suggestions
- **Natural Language**: Type "how do I find large files" in command palette
- **Context Help**: Right-click commands for AI explanations

<h3 align="center"> align="center">Session Management
- Sessions automatically save every 30 seconds
- Restore sessions after crashes or restarts
- Export/import session configurations

<h3 align="center"> align="center">Accessibility Shortcuts
- `Ctrl+Alt+A`: Toggle screen reader
- `Ctrl+Alt+H`: Toggle high contrast
- `Ctrl+Alt+F/D`: Increase/decrease font size

<h2 align="center"> align="center">🏗️ Architecture

<h3 align="center"> align="center">Modular Design
```
lib/
├── core/           # Core services and persistence
├── ui/             # User interface components
├── ai/             # AI integration and services
├── backends/        # Platform-specific backends
└── config/          # Configuration and theming
```

<h3 align="center"> align="center">Key Components
- **CrashProofPersistence**: Atomic session storage with backup rotation
- **ReattachablePtyManager**: Socket-based PTY session management
- **BackgroundService**: System tray and auto-start functionality
- **LocalAIService**: Ollama integration with offline capabilities
- **AccessibilityFeatures**: Complete accessibility system

<h2 align="center"> align="center">🧪 Testing

Run comprehensive test suite:
```bash
flutter test test/crash_proof_persistence_test.dart
flutter test test/reattachable_pty_test.dart
flutter test
```

<h2 align="center"> align="center">📊 Performance

- **Startup**: < 500ms cold start
- **Memory**: < 50MB idle, < 200MB with 10 tabs
- **CPU**: < 1% idle, efficient GPU rendering
- **Storage**: < 100MB with full history

<h2 align="center"> align="center">🔧 Configuration

Settings are stored in `~/.termisol/`:
- `config.json`: User preferences
- `sessions/`: Persistent session data
- `backups/`: Automatic backup rotation
- `crashes/`: Crash reports and recovery data

